Class Smarts2MQLVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.smiles.smarts.parser.visitor.Smarts2MQLVisitor

    public class Smarts2MQLVisitor
extends Object
implements SMARTSParserVisitor
    An AST tree visitor. It is a prototype that translate Smarts to MQL. It is far from fully functioning.
